# Language Convention

## Code & Files (English Only)

All generated code should use English for:
- Comments
- Variable/function names
- Log messages
- Error messages
- Documentation strings

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
// 获取用户信息
const 用户名 = "test";
logger.error('获取失败');

// ✅ GOOD
// Get user info
const username = "test";
logger.error('Failed to fetch user');
```

## Conversation (Chinese)

Reply to user in Chinese (中文回复).
